title: Grindhouse XXX: A Double Feature [Adam & Eve] (2011)
description: Starring: Alexis Ford, Briana Blair, Britney Amber, D Snoop, Derrick Pierce, India Summer, Nina Mercedes, Ralph Long, Rocco Reed, Seth Gamble, Teagan Presley Massacre at Pine Lake:It`s a universal law: large assemblies of horny young adults in the woods attract bloodthirsty psychos. Thus is the premise of Andre Madness` sexy and hysterical slasher flick, Massacre at Pine Lake. Head camp counselor Alexis Ford runs screaming from a serial killer, as he slices up her friends.Student Assassin:College student by day; killing machine by night! David Lord`s Student Assassin features Teagan Presley as a co-ed hellion bent on revenge.
